      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_8426125076692483929.png",
                "id": "talent31431",
                "key": "卷積微塵",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "卷積微塵"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/775a72af4465a157d3769ee561744b61_2982957921867113673.png",
                "id": "talent12978",
                "key": "風輪兩立",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風輪兩立"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">夜叉儺面</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">夜叉儺面</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>，且角色造成的<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行下落攻擊時：</span>傷害額外+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色為出戰角色，我方執行「切換角色」行動時：</span>少花費1個元素骰（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/447838f91bec368a2772f63aaa927c4c_4539708593335507092.png",
                "id": "talent57609",
                "key": "靖妖儺舞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "靖妖儺舞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點冰元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點水元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點火元素傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點雷元素傷害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_1634756632076744204.png",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">下落攻擊</span></strong></p><p>角色被切換為「出戰角色」後，本回合內的下一個戰鬥行動若為「普通攻擊」，則被視為「下落攻擊」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/26/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1900926107633583302.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
